{"title":"小城早晨","authors":["朱竹"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小城早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在新岁的绚丽中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在童话的馨香中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她穿起一件款式新颖的衣衫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袖口，飞出了鸽群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣兜，飞出了信息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掠过玫瑰色湖面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投入水灵灵花店"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后再去聆听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子上学沿途雀跃的足音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那条笔直的街——对襟线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天开始向她投影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的眸子——大玻璃窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向初升的太阳动情地一瞥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，所有的眼睛都亮了一下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的车轮都闪了一闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着小城的钮扣——街心花坛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向充实的一天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}